{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778980064739,"sessionID":"ses_1cc86d111ffeY08e3sGmsuZb8d","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"call_D2FLiaHZqcPkBHXklsqZPWPq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"obo-grep.pl --noheader -r 'GO:0052597|GO:0008131|GO:0004650|GO:0008473|EC:1.4.3.22|EC:1.4.3.13|EC:1.4.3.10|GO:0016641' src/ontology/go-edit.obo","timeout":120000,"workdir":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go","description":"Searches ontology for target terms"},"output":"[Term]\nid: GO:0001716\nname: L-amino-acid oxidase activity\nnamespace: molecular_function\ndef: \"Catalysis of the reaction: an L-alpha-amino acid + H2O + O2 = a 2-oxocarboxylate + H2O2 + NH4+.\" [RHEA:13781]\nsynonym: \"L-amino-acid:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)\" RELATED [EC:1.4.3.2]\nsynonym: \"ophio-amino-acid oxidase activity\" RELATED [EC:1.4.3.2]\nxref: EC:1.4.3.2 {source=\"skos:exactMatch\"}\nxref: MetaCyc:L-AMINO-ACID-OXIDASE-RXN\nxref: RHEA:13781 {source=\"skos:exactMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:19025 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:51404 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:60996 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61224 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61228 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61232 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61236 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61244 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61248 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61252 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61256 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61260 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61264 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61268 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61272 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61276 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61284 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nxref: RHEA:61344 {source=\"skos:narrowMatch\"}\nis_a: GO:0008131 ! primary methylamine oxidase activity\nproperty_value: term_tracker_item \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/